Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People are eating, so don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's better to see it with your own eyes than to hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka is finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, why are you girls screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, Valentine's is nearly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I doubt these festive youngsters will listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Valentine's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I nearly forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop pretending! Those lies won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.26,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You plan to make out while I'm not paying attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doing such indecent things at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, it's really pointless to give or receive chocolate at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}School is a place to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-We're being lectured by Haruta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then what's school for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Health care and PE, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, Aisaka-san, please come to the interview room after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, you still can't turn in your career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Aisaka-san, you haven't even turned one from first semester in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, I'm still discussing it with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your mother wants you to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko has{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My mother has always been a hard worker, but sometimes she pushes herself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to be a burden anymore, so I'm not planning on going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That is what I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So Aisaka-san, what's your reason for not turning it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I come from a rich family, so I won't ever need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's also why I don't need to study. Plus there's nothing I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I don't go to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand. It's just that you'll be on your own for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't just blame stuff on others. No one will take responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I want you two to carefully think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, you haven't gone against your mother's intentions, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After you've finished filling it out, bring it to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The rest of my life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, that's the career assessment form{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's impossible for me to think about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't even recognize myself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always, always denied my present self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Why is this happening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"What should I do to avoid it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I know what I want to do later when I don't even know what I want to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's one thing I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to fall in love normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You don't even have someone {\fscx300}-{\fscx100} no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone I like? I don't even know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to be born into a normal family, then raised as a normal good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then have a normal encounter with a guy and become friends normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to fall in love normally like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you using past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, the conditions are already wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not normal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean by "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's right and what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's there to decide on those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold it, why are you suddenly lecturing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, no... I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about the career assessments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home, I don't give a damn about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't I already refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always been{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But Kawashima, think about it one more{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have time to think about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, Kawashima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up and chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you want to do to my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have a shoe fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you trying to set a record for long throws at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why were you called to the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said I wouldn't model the school uniform for a school information pamphlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you refuse? Isn't that your speciality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't even know how much longer I'll be at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me that your fight with Kushieda{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, a trivial person like Kushieda Minori couldn't have an influence on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be honest, I planned to leave after first semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}News about the stalker thing has died down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never heard you mention{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I decided I wanted to stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to be with you guys tomorrow, or even the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I watched Taiga get hurt and understood her pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought that, since I understood her, I'd save her if no one else did, or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now I realize that everything would sort itself out if I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima, you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why now of all{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga? I'm really bu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My part-time job at the cake store too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They even made a cute uniform for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I contacted both places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just rest and don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yaa-chan is sleeping, shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, how's Yaa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank god, seeing her faint from my window scared the heck out of{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to buy something for Yasuko to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, Ryuuji! What about your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You left your cell phone, wallet and key! Your eco-bag too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get a grip on yourself, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, put it on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You too, why are you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm all right! You wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go home, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! You're acting all weird now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuj{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko fainted because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She has anemia! It's her body! It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.55,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I weren't that useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko would have more faith and trust in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She would rely on me more... then things like this would never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{w}Everything's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, everything's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything's all right, I'm a superb mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong? Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomorrow and the day after tomorrow are the busiest times because of Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, she really can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think I'll be able to find a substitute at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.61,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to do something for Yaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was fired from my part-time job at the cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's only normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure I'll be able to find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why are you comforting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say it with a stronger voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, your face wasn't born for advertising food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you guys are really working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruta-kun, which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They say if you buy big ones, bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll take that big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}May I have this one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-That'll be 580 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have an elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's not my sister, she's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, have fun with your jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you feel cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go to a warm place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.25,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world really has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Noto! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I just happened to pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah, has anyone else come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For example, Ami-chan, or even Nanako-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kihara didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? No! I don't really care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just wondering if Kihara will give Kitamura chocolate or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine with it either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, look, Taiga, you care about "that," don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? What do you mean by "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, why does Kihara Maya buying chocolate for Kitamura-kun concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I see. You like Kihara Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So people who realize their feelings after fighting really do exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.35,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.85,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-W-W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's so strange, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think it's strange at all. It's perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A male's stamen and a female's pistil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something wrong with your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll be scolded if we mess around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess there's no other choice than to summon the lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought you were by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, since you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, stupid Chihuahua, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No thanks. Don't make me do weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm beautiful, so I naturally grab people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, yes, you're beautiful! You're really attractive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you should take this and say "I love the chocolate here!" out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You want me to advertise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why would I do such a lame thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, how about you buy one for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You could give it to Minorin to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Contrary to popular belief, I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You want to get on good terms with Minorin, but it's not working out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The shaking delicate heart of a Chihuahua{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, why are you making assump{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're embarrassed, I'll call Minorin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, Valentine's Day came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, isn't that Kawashima Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right! She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her face is so slender!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's really Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she buying chocolate at that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love the chocolate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even my model friends say it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to buy the same kind as Ami-chan's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, she can be helpful from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, where are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me, I would like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You really like chasing after people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have potential to be a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You too, you like running away, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not just from me, but from a lot of other things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen, I don't think it'd be better if you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, you'll disappoint everyone if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone adores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, Taiga can't handle it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, I'd be happy even if it wasn't everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't get it myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks! I'll be counting on you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've reached our target already, so it's pointless to buy the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, I'm going to give them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I caused a lot of trouble for people on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like Kitamura-kun, and Minorin, and the stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I gave you chocolate, would you be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wouldn't be human if getting chocolate from you didn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just giving you guys store-bought chocolate is rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I'll try to do something nice with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hopefully I can make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, it smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're going to the shop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm all healthy now, so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to thank Taiga-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you bring us all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Today is Valentine's Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I made some chocolate to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You made it by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be such a waste to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasn't that the chocolate you were selling yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really good at telling lies{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The wrapping was nice so I reused it, but I made everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't help you with stuff like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yesterday was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next is Minorin's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know you went to save me during the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to be so formal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll come to save you whenever you're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you too, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Share it with Yaa-chan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next is Kitamura-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I put the most effort into this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, you were the person who carried me from the bottom of the cliff, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap, I didn't tell Kushieda to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if my eyes were all white...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really didn't expect that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I rolled down like this, and there were some weird noises in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I finally found out what fainting feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I felt like I blurted out things that I wasn't supposed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I regained my consciousness, I started to panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think you blurted out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't say it! I really can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin, I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't! Anyway, it was just my delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's something that no one should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be ruined if people find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be able to live anymore because it's something really, really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You didn't hear it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I heard nothing, right, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one heard anything, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think everything will be all right if you pretend you didn't hear it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What are you doing, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, you're glad that no one heard it because that solves everything, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun was the one who saved you, but he just didn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He didn't tell you because of what you said, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why... Why can't you just be honest for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, you look scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stupid Chihuahua...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think it'll be all right if you let Aisaka run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look here, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.11,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you see me as?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.09,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Minorin, your best friend, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:21:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't you say you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let go of me! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.52,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think you're the kind of person to blame others for your inability to go after what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or are you someone like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just want you to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just want the Minorin I love to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My happiness can only be.... can only be made with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My happiness doesn't depend on anyone but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami, are you betraying us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bad things will happen if you don't chase after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, I'll chase after Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not done talking with her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will happen if I chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will I do after I find out how Taiga feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She obviously wanted to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Taiga, it's about to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The laundry is still outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I left a lot of things out.
